1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,440
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="12"><b><font color="#0f100d">You Can't Be in a <font color="#29e1ef">Ro<font color="#ee3c51">m-<font color="#953db6">Co<font color="#f5a309">m <font color="#0f100d">
with Your Childhood Friends!</font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font></font></b></font>

2
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:05,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The four of you mean the world to me.</font>

3
00:00:05,690 --> 00:00:09,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would be weird 
for childhood friends like us</font>

4
00:00:09,950 --> 00:00:11,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to be in a rom-com situation, right?</font>

5
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have a childhood friend.</i></font>

6
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He usually acts cold, 
but he actually has a big heart.</i></font>

7
00:00:19,580 --> 00:00:23,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was an accident, 
but we even k-kissed...</i></font>

8
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>S-So...</i></font>

9
00:00:26,440 --> 00:00:29,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have a childhood friend.</i></font>

10
00:00:29,300 --> 00:00:31,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's a bit full of himself and stubborn,</i></font>

11
00:00:31,050 --> 00:00:34,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but he's dependable when it matters.</i></font>

12
00:00:34,340 --> 00:00:38,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to be more honest, too, but...</i></font>

13
00:00:39,400 --> 00:00:43,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Onii-chan is my childhood friend.</i></font>

14
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He always treats me 
like his little sister...</i></font>

15
00:00:46,300 --> 00:00:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But he must know how I feel about him!</i></font>

16
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So...</i></font>

17
00:00:53,140 --> 00:00:55,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have a childhood friend.</i></font>

18
00:00:56,210 --> 00:01:00,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's competitive and stubborn, 
but he's a precious friend.</i></font>

19
00:01:01,330 --> 00:01:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I said I'd support his love life, 
but at this rate...</i></font>

20
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:10,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Will this turn into a rom-com 
with a childhood friend?</i></font>

21
00:01:10,760 --> 00:01:15,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! I'm gonna dedicate 
this one to all of you!</font>

22
00:01:16,780 --> 00:01:18,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not even close?!</i></font>

23
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:24,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Up next is the coed three-legged race!</i></font>

24
00:01:24,520 --> 00:01:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will it develop into a lovely romance?!</font>

25
00:01:27,530 --> 00:01:30,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Good luck everyone!</i></font>

26
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:30,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Akari.</font>

27
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The person I was paired with got hurt, 
so I was looking for a sub.</font>

28
00:01:35,330 --> 00:01:36,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, whatever.</font>

29
00:01:36,780 --> 00:01:39,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why did you choose me?</font>

30
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a gap in height and you know 
I'm not the best... runner...</font>

31
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:46,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

32
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my precious 
childhood friend, remember?</font>

33
00:01:49,410 --> 00:01:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Teehee!</font>

34
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gross!</font>

35
00:01:51,270 --> 00:01:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough with that face!</font>

36
00:01:52,790 --> 00:01:54,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay away from me!</font>

37
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}All right! I'm gonna give it my all!</font>

38
00:01:54,340 --> 00:01:59,010
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#da62cc">twist</font></b></font>

39
00:01:54,340 --> 00:01:59,010
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#da62cc">twist</font></b></font>

40
00:01:57,070 --> 00:01:59,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Gross! Don't move like that!</font>

41
00:01:59,010 --> 00:02:01,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so excited!</font>

42
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:04,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't you ask Shio? 
She's a childhood friend, too.</font>

43
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:07,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio's busy with committee member duties,</font>

44
00:02:05,270 --> 00:02:11,650
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#4e4470">Executive Committee Member</font></font></font></b></font>

45
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:09,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru's White Team,</font>

46
00:02:07,650 --> 00:02:11,650
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#4e4470">White Team</font></font></font></b></font>

47
00:02:09,530 --> 00:02:11,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Runako's in junior high.</font>

48
00:02:09,530 --> 00:02:11,650
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#4e4470">Junior High Student</font></font></font></b></font>

49
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:14,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it's only because 
there's no one else.</font>

50
00:02:14,630 --> 00:02:15,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's not.</font>

51
00:02:16,410 --> 00:02:18,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to run with you, Akari.</font>

52
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are my precious 
childhood friend, after all!</font>

53
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So gross!</font>

54
00:02:27,410 --> 00:02:29,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do anything you want 
to return the favor!</font>

55
00:02:31,170 --> 00:02:32,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything?</font>

56
00:02:40,310 --> 00:02:45,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}All right, participants, 
please take your positions!</i></font>

57
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dummy! What am I thinking?!</i></font>

58
00:02:48,790 --> 00:02:50,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey!</font>

59
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:52,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Akari. Put your hand on my waist.</font>

60
00:02:52,990 --> 00:02:56,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gosh, I can't stop thinking about it.</i></font>

61
00:02:57,100 --> 00:02:59,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My heart is...</i></font>

62
00:03:00,370 --> 00:03:03,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on, Akari?
Are you nervous?</font>

63
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:06,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What do you care?</font>

64
00:03:06,410 --> 00:03:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your body feels stiff. Are you okay?</font>

65
00:03:09,130 --> 00:03:11,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Too close! Too close!
Too close!</i></font>

66
00:03:11,310 --> 00:03:14,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Calm down and take a deep breath.</font>

67
00:03:14,010 --> 00:03:17,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>S-So annoying.
He's acting like it's no big deal.</i></font>

68
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:21,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would be weird 
for childhood friends like us</font>

69
00:03:22,270 --> 00:03:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to be in a rom-com situation, right?</font>

70
00:03:24,810 --> 00:03:27,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So he's telling me 
I'm not even on his radar?</i></font>

71
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready...</font>

72
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:31,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shoot! I'm not mentally ready yet...</i></font>

73
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Set...</font>

74
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:35,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akari, start with your right foot!</font>

75
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:38,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

76
00:03:39,330 --> 00:03:43,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All right! Taking the lead at the start 
is team Sakai and Hiodoshi!</i></font>

77
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? It's easy to run...</i></font>

78
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:50,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those two are totally in sync!</font>

79
00:03:50,020 --> 00:03:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amazing!</font>

80
00:03:51,580 --> 00:03:55,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is Eiyu... matching my pace?</i></font>

81
00:03:55,270 --> 00:03:59,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Oh no! But they aren't 
picking up the pace!</i></font>

82
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:01,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm really bad at running!</i></font>

83
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:03,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're behind now.</font>

84
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:05,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is he doing?</font>

85
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:07,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're perfectly in sync, though.</font>

86
00:04:07,340 --> 00:04:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan...</font>

87
00:04:09,030 --> 00:04:10,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu...</font>

88
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:13,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay, Akari.</font>

89
00:04:13,650 --> 00:04:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's keep going at our own pace.</font>

90
00:04:15,900 --> 00:04:17,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Step by step, okay?</font>

91
00:04:18,530 --> 00:04:20,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all about having fun!</font>

92
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:26,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe it's okay like this...</i></font>

93
00:04:26,050 --> 00:04:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If Eiyu's this kind, 
I can be more honest...</i></font>

94
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't have to be all about winning.</font>

95
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ugh! Darn it!</i></font>

96
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One more! One more time!</font>

97
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gosh, not this again!</font>

98
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your mom will get mad!</font>

99
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:50,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotcha!</font>

100
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu!</font>

101
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care!</font>

102
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna keep going until I win!</font>

103
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:02,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You may not win till you die!</font>

104
00:05:03,140 --> 00:05:06,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll keep going until 
I win, even if it kills me!</font>

105
00:05:06,450 --> 00:05:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gosh!</font>

106
00:05:06,450 --> 00:05:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Not a chance!</font>

107
00:05:08,670 --> 00:05:10,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You brat!</font>

108
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a dummy.</font>

109
00:05:25,140 --> 00:05:30,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Wow! Team Sakai and Hiodoshi 
have suddenly ramped up the pace!</i></font>

110
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akari?</font>

111
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

112
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:34,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're totally out of sync now!</font>

113
00:05:34,630 --> 00:05:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

114
00:05:35,980 --> 00:05:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're totally out of sync, but they're 
moving up steadily from the very back!</font>

115
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Could this be a big comeback?!</i></font>

116
00:05:42,430 --> 00:05:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're so fast!</font>

117
00:05:45,450 --> 00:05:48,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akari, you've got so much energy!</font>

118
00:05:49,850 --> 00:05:51,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it...!</font>

119
00:05:53,610 --> 00:05:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop laughing and keep up!</font>

120
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akari?</font>

121
00:05:58,210 --> 00:05:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with you?!</font>

122
00:05:59,380 --> 00:06:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usually you'd say, "Don't start running 
all of a sudden," or, "Match my pace"!</font>

123
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you have anything to say?!</font>

124
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just being my usual self.</font>

125
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No you're not!</font>

126
00:06:11,230 --> 00:06:12,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You never just agree!</font>

127
00:06:12,730 --> 00:06:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so full of yourself and so cocky!</font>

128
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:19,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Always acting tough, stupid, 
short-sighted, and ridiculously stubborn!</font>

129
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akari, you sure know a lot about me.</font>

130
00:06:23,450 --> 00:06:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But!</font>

131
00:06:25,740 --> 00:06:27,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even after all that...</font>

132
00:06:28,220 --> 00:06:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like you!</font>

133
00:06:30,790 --> 00:06:32,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Akari...</font>

134
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:00,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh my!</i></font>

135
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:05,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Team Sakai and Hiodoshi 
have fallen to the ground!</i></font>

136
00:07:05,740 --> 00:07:08,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're totally behind now!</i></font>

137
00:07:11,790 --> 00:07:13,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?</font>

138
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get off of me.</font>

139
00:07:16,930 --> 00:07:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not letting you have this 
as you are now.</font>

140
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:23,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akari-chan, are you okay?</font>

141
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:24,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm okay.</font>

142
00:07:25,660 --> 00:07:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, get up already.</font>

143
00:07:28,370 --> 00:07:30,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's finish this run!</font>

144
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:35,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gross mode!</i></font>

145
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:35,180
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Impact"><b><font size="40"><font color="#f687cc">GROSS MODE</font></font></b></font></b></font>

146
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:35,180
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Impact"><b><font size="40"><font color="#ca7edf">GROSS MODE</font></font></b></font></b></font>

147
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:35,180
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Impact"><b><font size="40"><font color="#6e64e6">GROSS MODE</font></font></b></font></b></font>

148
00:07:35,180 --> 00:07:40,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The pair that went down is back up 
and sprinting toward the goal!</i></font>

149
00:07:40,570 --> 00:07:41,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Goal!</i></font>

150
00:07:41,930 --> 00:07:44,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The pair reached 
the goal together, in sync!</i></font>

151
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:50,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This concludes the morning event, 
and it is now lunchtime.</i></font>

152
00:07:50,550 --> 00:07:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The afternoon event will begin at 1:15PM,</i></font>

153
00:07:53,790 --> 00:07:56,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}starting with the girl's obstacle course.</i></font>

154
00:07:54,550 --> 00:07:56,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good job, Akari!</font>

155
00:07:57,020 --> 00:08:02,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Participants, please gather 
at Tent #1 by 1PM.</i></font>

156
00:07:57,020 --> 00:07:59,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But are you sure you're okay?</font>

157
00:07:59,510 --> 00:08:02,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was quite a fall.</font>

158
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm totally fine!</font>

159
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about it.</font>

160
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, my childhood friends!</font>

161
00:08:15,570 --> 00:08:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You all worked so hard this morning!</font>

162
00:08:18,060 --> 00:08:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, let's all eat lunch together!</font>

163
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Cringe... cringe...</i></font>

164
00:08:20,150 --> 00:08:22,610
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#3b3ea6">cringe</font></b></font></b></font>

165
00:08:20,150 --> 00:08:22,610
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#3b3ea6">cringe</font></b></font></b></font>

166
00:08:20,150 --> 00:08:22,610
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#3b3ea6">cringe</font></b></font></b></font>

167
00:08:20,150 --> 00:08:22,610
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#3b3ea6">cringe</font></b></font></b></font>

168
