respond to this challenge?</font>

344
00:17:10,180 --> 00:17:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll just choose someone as a... joke...</i></font>

345
00:17:14,010 --> 00:17:18,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Someone you really, really, 
really, </i>really<i> love!"</i></font>

346
00:17:18,390 --> 00:17:21,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who will he choose?</i></font>

347
00:17:26,520 --> 00:17:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sakai-kun is running!</i></font>

348
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:31,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did he make up his mind?!</i></font>

349
00:17:32,120 --> 00:17:33,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Runako...</i></font>

350
00:17:35,530 --> 00:17:37,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Akari... Shio...</i></font>

351
00:17:40,190 --> 00:17:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Haru!</i></font>

352
00:17:41,500 --> 00:17:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I choose...</i></font>

353
00:17:51,990 --> 00:17:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako! Come with me!</font>

354
00:17:54,460 --> 00:17:56,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan!</font>

355
00:17:56,500 --> 00:17:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one he really loves...</font>

356
00:17:59,020 --> 00:18:00,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Runako?</font>

357
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:01,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No...</i></font>

358
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>H-Huh? Why am I disappointed?</i></font>

359
00:18:05,270 --> 00:18:06,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

360
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:09,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay! But wait, Onii-chan?!</font>

361
00:18:11,870 --> 00:18:14,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan, you know...</font>

362
00:18:17,530 --> 00:18:19,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Squeeze!</font>

363
00:18:20,460 --> 00:18:22,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you doing?!</font>

364
00:18:22,990 --> 00:18:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is your heart racing?</font>

365
00:18:25,840 --> 00:18:28,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or do you feel at ease?</font>

366
00:18:28,040 --> 00:18:29,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

367
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:33,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feeling naughty, yet 
wanting to cherish someone...</font>

368
00:18:33,470 --> 00:18:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay to feel all of that!</font>

369
00:18:45,630 --> 00:18:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You too, Akari!</font>

370
00:18:46,790 --> 00:18:48,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

371
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:51,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You too, Shio!</font>

372
00:18:51,210 --> 00:18:52,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

373
00:18:57,750 --> 00:18:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru, you too, come with me!</font>

374
00:18:59,020 --> 00:19:00,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Me too?</font>

375
00:19:01,130 --> 00:19:04,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What's going on here?</font>

376
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:09,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakai-kun has selected 
<i>four</i> beauties from the crowd!</font>

377
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:12,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}They're all heading for the goal!</i></font>

378
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:13,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's just how it is...</i></font>

379
00:19:13,860 --> 00:19:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with childhood friends.</font>

380
00:19:17,640 --> 00:19:19,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see...</i></font>

381
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:22,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So it's okay to both have horny feelings 
and to want to cherish them.</i></font>

382
00:19:24,020 --> 00:19:26,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It all makes sense now.</i></font>

383
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:31,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was confused and
didn't know what to do...</i></font>

384
00:19:31,600 --> 00:19:32,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But!</i></font>

385
00:19:32,530 --> 00:19:33,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio!</font>

386
00:19:34,650 --> 00:19:36,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akari!</font>

387
00:19:36,650 --> 00:19:38,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako!</font>

388
00:19:38,660 --> 00:19:39,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru!</font>

389
00:19:40,840 --> 00:19:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've known the answer for a long time!</i></font>

390
00:19:45,380 --> 00:19:47,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My childhood friends are...</i></font>

391
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Goal!</i></font>

392
00:19:50,850 --> 00:19:56,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakai-kun of Red Team makes 
the goal with four beauties!</font>

393
00:19:56,130 --> 00:19:59,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, the final judgment!</font>

394
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Now, I'll check your slip.</font>

395
00:20:03,180 --> 00:20:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

396
00:20:04,390 --> 00:20:10,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really, really, 
<i>really</i> love everyone here?</font>

397
00:20:12,320 --> 00:20:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know!</font>

398
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:15,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But!</font>

399
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:20,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're all my precious childhood friends!</font>

400
00:20:25,580 --> 00:20:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now, what's the much-anticipated decision?</i></font>

401
00:20:31,500 --> 00:20:33,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Accepted!</i></font>

402
00:20:33,710 --> 00:20:36,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Victory goes to Red Team!</i></font>

403
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:39,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An incredible last-minute victory!</i></font>

404
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for your help!
I got first place!</font>

405
00:20:48,380 --> 00:20:50,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gotta be kidding me!</font>

406
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:51,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">White Team lost!</font>

407
00:20:51,600 --> 00:20:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was really misleading!</font>

408
00:20:51,600 --> 00:20:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Congrats on first place!</font>

409
00:20:51,600 --> 00:20:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Gosh, you scared me!</font>

410
00:20:55,740 --> 00:20:58,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're okay with that, Eiyu?</font>

411
00:20:59,780 --> 00:21:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gross Eiyu.</font>

412
00:21:01,830 --> 00:21:03,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're sure, right?</font>

413
00:21:03,790 --> 00:21:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't say I'm sure.</font>

414
00:21:06,060 --> 00:21:10,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I want to be honest with my feelings.</font>

415
00:21:17,030 --> 00:21:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even the horny feelings...</font>

416
00:21:20,280 --> 00:21:21,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

417
00:21:22,260 --> 00:21:24,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, good luck.</font>

418
00:21:25,440 --> 00:21:27,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan? What's wrong?</font>

419
00:21:27,860 --> 00:21:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing. Thanks, Runako.</font>

420
00:21:32,300 --> 00:21:35,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>See ya, Gross Eiyu.</i></font>

421
00:21:48,230 --> 00:21:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

422
00:21:50,590 --> 00:21:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't eat anymore...</font>

423
00:21:53,290 --> 00:21:56,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan, wake up...</font>

424
00:21:57,470 --> 00:21:59,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two!</font>

425
00:21:59,170 --> 00:22:02,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cut it out!</font>

426
00:22:02,850 --> 00:22:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, let me go!</font>

427
00:22:05,040 --> 00:22:06,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

428
00:22:06,580 --> 00:22:08,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Akari?</font>

429
00:22:08,670 --> 00:22:10,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?</font>

430
00:22:12,430 --> 00:22:14,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get the wrong idea.</font>

431
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:17,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't waiting for you at all.</font>

432
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Haru?</font>

433
00:22:24,010 --> 00:22:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}H-Hey, what a coincidence!</font>

434
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:28,510
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<b><font color="#ffffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="10">Translator:
Timer:
Editor:
Quality Control:
Final Quality Control:</font></font></font></b></b></font>

435
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:28,510
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<b><font color="#ffffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="10">Sachiko Takahashi
Mariana Martinez
Gabriella Alabanza
S Bilyeu
Rei Miyasaka</font></font></font></b></b></font>

436
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:28,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A coincidence?</font>

437
00:22:28,510 --> 00:22:30,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's your bike,
Haru-kun?</font>

438
00:22:31,100 --> 00:22:32,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, um, a flat...</font>

439
00:22:32,580 --> 00:22:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got a flat tire, so...</font>

440
00:22:33,410 --> 00:22:36,080
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#266bbc">stare</font></b></font>

441
00:22:33,410 --> 00:22:36,080
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#266bbc">stare</font></b></font>

442
00:22:36,080 --> 00:22:40,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}A-Anyway, you're all going to school 
all lovey-dovey as usual, huh?</font>

443
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

444
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Not at all!</font>

445
00:22:43,270 --> 00:22:44,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right!</font>

446
00:22:46,560 --> 00:22:48,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you must be feeling 
all horny already, right?</font>

447
00:22:48,970 --> 00:22:50,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu?!</font>

448
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You're all my precious 
childhood friends.</font>

449
00:22:55,650 --> 00:22:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-All I'm feeling is bliss.</font>

450
00:22:59,610 --> 00:23:00,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

451
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gross!</font>

452
00:23:01,070 --> 00:23:03,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you going Gross Eiyu again?!</font>

453
00:23:03,810 --> 00:23:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't!</font>

454
00:23:06,660 --> 00:23:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before he does...</font>

455
00:23:08,450 --> 00:23:09,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's run!</font>

456
00:23:11,750 --> 00:23:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have four
childhood friends.</i></font>

457
00:23:17,670 --> 00:23:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Huh? Oh, hey!</font>

458
00:23:18,170 --> 00:23:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The childhood friends 
in fiction are all fake.</i></font>

459
00:23:23,050 --> 00:23:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I know what real life is like!</i></font>

460
00:23:25,860 --> 00:23:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You can't be in a rom-com...</i></font>

461
00:23:29,540 --> 00:23:31,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}with your childhood friends!</i></font>

462
00:23:31,960 --> 00:23:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now what?</font>

463
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:33,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at him.</font>

464
00:23:33,700 --> 00:23:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan...</font>

465
00:23:34,740 --> 00:23:35,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's he doing?</font>

466
00:23:35,790 --> 00:23:37,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's so flustered!</font>

467
00:23:37,640 --> 00:23:39,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at him, he's so flustered.</font>

468
00:23:40,650 --> 00:23:43,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Or maybe you can! Who knows?!</i></font>

469
00:23:41,190 --> 00:23:46,200
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="12"><font color="#fdffff">Episode 12</font></font></b></font></b></font>

470
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:46,200
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#fdfdfd">Did the Three-Legged Race and Feel a Little Naughty?</font></font></font></b></font>

471
00:23:42,020 --> 00:23:46,200
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#fdfdfd">Then Doing the Scavenger Hunt Still Won't Start a <font size="22"><font color="#10c7e6">Ro<font color="#f13d50">m-<font color="#9341b3">Co<font color="#f8a103">m</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

472
00:23:46,530 --> 00:23:50,070
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="18"><b><font color="#0f100d">You Can't Be in a <font color="#29e1ef">Ro<font color="#ee3c51">m-<font color="#953db6">Co<font color="#f5a309">m <font color="#0f100d">
with Your Childhood Friends!</font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font></font></b></font>

